<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Our Services | ProduceBridge</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'services', media: 'all' %> 
</head>
<body>
    <div class="services-container">
        <!-- Page Title -->
        <h1>Our Services</h1>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <p>At <strong>ProduceBridge</strong>, we offer services aimed at reducing food waste and supporting sustainable agriculture. Our goal is to connect organizations with surplus food to those who can use it effectively, creating a positive impact on both the environment and the community.</p>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <div class="feature-section">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Biowaste to Feed</h3>
                <p>We collect surplus food and process it into nutritious animal feed, reducing waste and supporting local farms.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Compost Creation</h3>
                <p>Our program transforms organic waste into rich compost that nourishes the soil and promotes sustainable agriculture.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Natural Fertilizer</h3>
                <p>By recycling food waste, we produce eco-friendly fertilizers that help farmers grow healthier, more resilient crops.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Detailed Service Descriptions -->
        <h2>Who We Serve</h2>

        <h3>Grocery Stores</h3>
        <p><strong>Reduce Waste:</strong> Effectively manage excess inventory.</p>
        <p><strong>Community Impact:</strong> Support local food pantries and reduce food insecurity.</p>

        <h3>Farms</h3>
        <p><strong>Utilize Surplus:</strong> Connect with organizations that can use unsold produce.</p>
        <p><strong>Increase Revenue:</strong> Offset losses by finding new channels for surplus goods.</p>
        <p><strong>Offset Feed Costs:</strong> Use unsaleable or expired produce to reduce livestock feed costs.</p>

        <h3>Truck Drivers</h3>
        <p><strong>Avoid Losses:</strong> Find organizations that can take rejected loads and reduce wasted miles.</p>
        <p><strong>Support Local:</strong> Help feed communities while maximizing your delivery routes.</p>

        <h3>Food Pantries and Nonprofits</h3>
        <p><strong>Access Quality Food:</strong> Get fresh, surplus food to distribute to those in need.</p>
        <p><strong>Strengthen Community Ties:</strong> Build relationships with local businesses and farms.</p>

        <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
        <div class="cta-section">
            <h2>Ready to Join Us?</h2>
            <p>ProduceBridge is more than a service; itâ€™s a movement toward a sustainable and equitable food system. Together, we can reduce waste and make a difference.</p>
            <%= link_to "Get Involved", contact_path, class: "cta-button" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
